_sText:
This is the final version of my initial map release (http://gamebanana.com/csszm/maps/166056).

+ Fixed cubemap lighting issues.
+ Lots of cosmetic changes.
+ Reduced size of map by a few hundred units.
+ Added more props and breakable areas to make gameplay fair.
+ Removed fog and rotating helicopter to increase FPS.
+ Added teleports to all parts of the map to allow going between the outside and inside areas quickly.
+ Redesigned and added more cade rooms in the building across the jail cells.
+ Fixed annoying looped elevator sound and increased the speed of the elevator for faster transportation.
